node.text: I’ve been meaning to do one of these forever and finally did... I was holding my breath the whole time and feeling awkward but here it is😅 this is how I wind down when I am anxious or groundless. P.S literally none of this is an ad, just products by brands I love :) xx take care of yourselves 🌿🌸
